STYLE BINDING

- variation of property binding
- very similar to class bindingf.
- eg,
    <button [style.backgroundColor]="isActive ? 'red' : 'white'">Delete</button>

    export class SomeClass{
        //
        status = true;
        //
    }

- for a list of style object: https://www.w3schools.com/jsref/dom_obj_style.asp